            "diff_url": "https://github.com/python/cpython/pull/130101.diff",
            "patch_url": "https://github.com/python/cpython/pull/130101.patch",
            "merged_at": "2025-02-18T23:02:42Z"
          },
          "body": "Entries may be added or removed from `sys.meta_path` concurrently. For example, setuptools temporarily adds and removes the `distutils` finder from the beginning of the list. The local copy ensures that we don't skip over any entries.\r\n\r\nSome packages modify `sys.modules` during import. For example, `collections` inserts the entry for `collections.abc`  into `sys.modules` during import. We need to ensure that we re-check `sys.modules` *after* the parent module is fully initialized.\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- gh-issue-number: gh-130094 -->\r\n* Issue: gh-130094\r\n<!-- /gh-issue-number -->\r\n",
          "closed_by": {
